'''列斯·布基'''（{{lang-en|'''Reece Burke'''}}，{{bd|1996年|9月2日|catIdx=Burke, Reece}}）<ref name=whufc2>{{cite web|url=http://www.whufc.com/articles/20110715/youths-201011_2236884_2395268|title=Youths 2010/11|accessdate=19 December 2011|date=15 July 2011|publisher=West Ham United F.C.|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131224112903/http://www.whufc.com/articles/20110715/youths-201011_2236884_2395268|archivedate=2013年12月24日}}</ref>是一名[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]職業足球員，現時效力[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|英冠]]球會[[卢顿足球俱乐部|盧頓]]，司職[[後衛_(足球)|後衛]]。列斯·布基曾效力於[[英格蘭18歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭18歲以下足球代表隊]]。雖然他主要位置中堅，但是他還可以客串右後衛。

==生平==
===球會===
;韋斯咸
伯克九歲時已加盟韋斯咸的青年隊<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.whufc.com/articles/reece-burke-west-ham_2228487_68832 | title=Reece Burke | publisher=www.whufc.com | accessdate=16 January 2014 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140106074209/http://www.whufc.com/articles/reece-burke-west-ham_2228487_68832 | archivedate=2014年1月6日 }}</ref>。他的首次上陣是於2014年1月5日在[[足總杯|足總杯]]賽事在[[城市足球場|城市足球場]]迎戰[[諾定咸森林足球會|諾定咸森林]]。森林在這埸比賽贏了5-0<ref>{{cite news|title=Nottm Forest 5 v 0 West Ham|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/25539803|accessdate=5 January 2014|publisher=BBC Sport|date=5 January 2014|archive-date=2015-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150809062408/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/25539803|dead-url=no}}</ref>。伯克為球會射入的第一個入球出現在季前友誼賽在[[烏普頓公園球場|博林球場]]迎戰[[森多利亞足球會|森多利亞]]。他在第90分鐘接應他的青年隊隊友 [[埃利奧特·李爾|埃利奧特·李爾]]的傳中球射入制勝的一球<ref>{{cite web | title=West Ham United 3–2 Sampdoria: Reece Burke notches winner in five-goal thriller to give Sam Allardyce first win of pre-season | url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2720666/West-Ham-United-3-2-Sampdoria-Reece-Burke-notches-winner-Mark-Noble-Mohamed-Diame-net.html | publisher=Daily Mail | accessdate=9 August 2014 | archive-date=2020-11-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112015423/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2720666/West-Ham-United-3-2-Sampdoria-Reece-Burke-notches-winner-Mark-Noble-Mohamed-Diame-net.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。伯克然後在[[聯賽杯|聯賽杯]]第二輪對戰[[錫菲聯|錫菲聯]]的賽事打足120分鐘，可惜韋斯咸在[[互射十二碼|互射十二碼]]被淘汰<ref>{{cite web | title=West Ham 1–1 Sheff Utd | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/28847232 | publisher=BBC Sport | accessdate=27 August 2014 | archive-date=2015-11-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151125003555/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/28847232 | dead-url=no }}</ref> 。伯克於2015年4月25日首次在英超上陣，韋斯咸最終以0-0和[[昆士柏流浪|昆士柏流浪]]<ref name="PremDebut ">{{cite web | url=http://www1.skysports.com/football/live/match/313723/report | title=QPR 0–0 West Ham | publisher=Sky Sports | accessdate=25 April 2015 | archive-date=2015-05-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518064426/http://www1.skysports.com/football/live/match/313723/report | dead-url=no }}</ref>。伯克於2015年5月6日當選為2014-15年度“韋斯咸最佳年輕球員”<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-3071109/West-Ham-Player-Awards-Aaron-Cresswell-wins-hat-trick-gongs-including-Hammer-Year-Players-Player-year.html |title=West Ham Player Awards: Aaron Cresswell wins hat-trick of gongs including Hammer of the Year and Players' Player of the year {{!}} Daily Mail Online<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2015-05-25 |archive-date=2016-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160605113544/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-3071109/West-Ham-Player-Awards-Aaron-Cresswell-wins-hat-trick-gongs-including-Hammer-Year-Players-Player-year.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

